Package: hhss
Type: Package
Title: Hunter Harvest Survey Simulations
Version: 1.0.0
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports: 
    dplyr (>= 1.0.0), 
    purrr,
    stats
Author: Peter Donati
Maintainer: Peter Donati <p.donati11@gmail.com>
Description: Simulates populations of hunters and harvest survey responses for 
    common survey methodologies. Methods include simple random sample,
    mandatory reporting, and voluntary reporting. Creates estimates of total
    harvest and reports error compared to true harvests, as well as other useful
    summary statistics.
